title: 13-Year-Old ‘Cash Me Outside’ Girl And Her Friends Involved In Brawl Outside Of Bar
text:
13-year-old Danielle Bregoli aka the ‘Cash me outside” girl sure does know how to find trouble. 
According to TMZ, Danielle and her friends were outside of a bar and got into a yelling match with several hecklers nearby. That’s when one of Danielle’s friend walked up to a girl and started to drag her by hair. All hell broke loose after that as the girls scattered away. 

What is this 13-year-old girl doing near a bar at night? Where is her mother?
